OL,3,C'I've had death threats': Muslim women
OL,4,Creflect as UN vows to combat
OL,5,CIslamophobia
OL,7,FBy Zahra Manji, ITV News Assistant
OL,8,FNews Editor
OL,10,F"I've had serious death threats, I've
OL,11,Fhad threats to kidnap me and threats
OL,12,Fof sexual violence."
OL,14,FApsana Begum MP is no stranger to
OL,15,Fdiscrimination. As a visibly Muslim
OL,16,Fwoman living in the UK, and the first
OL,17,Fand only hijab-wearing MP, she has
OL,18,Fendured both Islamophobic and
OL,19,Fmisogynistic attacks.
