OL,3,C'I've had death threats': Muslim women
OL,4,Creflect as UN vows to combat
OL,5,CIslamophobia
OL,7,FThose who are visibly Muslim often
OL,8,Ffeel the brunt of anti-Muslim hate,
OL,9,Fbombarded by racist stereotypes and
OL,10,Fsubjected to societal inequalities.
OL,12,FITV News spoke to three prominent
OL,13,FMuslim women, each pioneers in their
OL,14,Ffield, about what it's like to be
OL,15,Fvisibly Muslim in a society where hate
OL,16,Fcrime is on the rise.
OL,18,F"When I started wearing the hijab, I
OL,19,Fdidn't see anybody like myself in
OL,20,FParliament," Apsana, MP for Poplar and
OL,21,FLimehouse, reflected.
