OL,7,FAssumptions were often made about her
OL,8,Fas soon as she entered political
OL,9,Frooms, but this didn't deter her from
OL,10,Fentering public office.
OL,12,F"I endured a series of racist attacks,
OL,13,Fwhilst on my campaign trail, and it
OL,14,Fwas really quite horrendous," she
OL,15,Fsaid, with threats to rip off her
OL,16,Fhijab in public.
