OL,7,FShe felt the trolling had been
OL,8,Flegitimised by the prime minister at
OL,9,Fthe time, Boris Johnson, who had
OL,10,Fpreviously said Muslim women wearing
OL,11,Fburqas "looked like letter boxes".
OL,13,FHis comments had proven to have
OL,14,Fdirectly correlated to a 300% increase
OL,15,Fin hate crimes towards Muslims. She
OL,16,Fwas shocked with the abuse but said
OL,17,Fshe's "immune to it now because it got
OL,18,Fso much."
