OL,7,FThe ongoing security threats had
OL,8,Fcaused Apsana to consider not
OL,9,Fcontinuing but knew she had a "strong
OL,10,Fresponsibility and duty" to the
OL,11,Funderrepresented.
OL,13,FShe feels that being the first and
OL,14,Fonly hijab-wearing MP is a huge
OL,15,Fmilestone.
OL,17,F"It's an achievement in terms of
OL,18,Fdiversity and inclusion in Parliament,
OL,19,Fand I think that should be celebrated,
OL,20,Fand valued.
