OL,7,F"We need to challenge these narratives
OL,8,Fhead on and create a safe space for
OL,9,Feach other."
OL,11,FWith such deep-rooted stereotypes, it
OL,12,Fcan also deter aspiring athletes from
OL,13,Fpursuing their goals and careers.
OL,15,FFormer semi-pro footballer and sport
OL,16,Factivist, Lipa Nessa, said she wants
OL,17,Fto change the world "with a hijab on
OL,18,Fher head and a ball at her feet."
