OL,7,FLipa started wearing hijab when she
OL,8,Fwas 15 and soon saw a noticeable
OL,9,Fdifference on the pitch.
OL,11,F"As soon as I looked different, I was
OL,12,Falienated. My name is not a very
OL,13,FMuslim name, so it was never an issue
OL,14,Funtil I decided to wear it and people
OL,15,Frealised, 'Oh, she's a Muslim. And
OL,16,Fshe's a visible Muslim.'
OL,18,F"I did stick out like a sore thumb,
OL,19,Fand it subtly educated me that not
OL,20,Feveryone likes us."
