OL,7,FShe faced abuse from coaches and even
OL,8,Fspectators.
OL,10,F"During my first away game the
OL,11,Fopposition's parents made aeroplane
OL,12,Fnoises and booed me every time I
OL,13,Freceived the ball... I was still a
OL,14,Fchild," she remembered.
OL,16,FLipa was even told to take "that
OL,17,Fstupid thing off" her head by a coach
OL,18,Fshe had previously considered a friend.
