OL,7,F"We should be judged on merit, but
OL,8,Funfortunately we live in a society
OL,9,Fwhere looks matter," she said.
OL,11,FShe suddenly felt like she didn't
OL,12,Fbelong in the world of sport, a world
OL,13,Fshe had loved for so long.
OL,15,F"Football became forced rather than
OL,16,Ffun. I started asking myself how to
OL,17,Fget out of training. Can I fake an
OL,18,Finjury?"
