OL,7,FIt wasn't until Lipa moved to a more
OL,8,Fdiverse team with a younger, more
OL,9,Feducated coach that she began to feel
OL,10,Faccepted and discover her love for
OL,11,Ffootball again.
OL,13,F"It was so refreshing; I didn't have
OL,14,Fto apologise for being me."
OL,16,FShe has since been a champion for
OL,17,Finclusivity on the pitch, launching a
OL,18,Fnew sports hijab with the Sweaty Betty
OL,19,FFoundation.
