OL,7,FFor Lipa, educating people and working
OL,8,Fwith allies is the first step to
OL,9,Fchanging the negative narrative of
OL,10,FMuslims in sport.
OL,12,FScotland's first hijab-wearing
OL,13,Freporter, Tasnim Nazeer, also started
OL,14,Fwearing hijab in her teens and noticed
OL,15,Fday-to-day differences.
OL,17,F"People were just more irritable," she
OL,18,Fsaid. One encounter in Glasgow saw a
OL,19,Fdrunk man follow her and her children,
OL,20,Fswearing at them and calling them
OL,21,Fterrorists.
