OL,7,FDiscrimination continued into her
OL,8,Fcareer with one colleague telling her
OL,9,Fthat she would be further down the
OL,10,Fline as a reporter if she didn't wear
OL,11,Fher hijab.
OL,13,F"We have to work twice as hard to get
OL,14,Fa seat around the table," she told ITV
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,FTasnim feels there are still problems
OL,18,Fin mainstream visual representation
OL,19,Fafter one social media user said, "we
OL,20,Fdon't want to see that rag, take it
OL,21,Foff", after she came off air.
