OL,7,FBut despite the aggressions and
OL,8,Fdiscouragement, she believes the
OL,9,Fpresence of Muslim women should be
OL,10,Ffelt, especially in newsrooms where
OL,11,Fdiverse voices are fundamental.
OL,13,F"We're not nurtured in the same way as
OL,14,Four peers," she said. "If it's
OL,15,Fdiversity and inclusion that
OL,16,Fmainstream organisations want, they
OL,17,Fhave to give people a chance."
