OL,7,FAfter speaking to these women about
OL,8,Ftheir journeys into their respective
OL,9,Findustries, a running theme became
OL,10,Fapparent.
OL,12,FThey all concluded that they would
OL,13,Fnever compromise their faith for their
OL,14,Fcareer, but instead use it as
OL,15,Fmotivation to break barriers for
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,F"It's a woman's choice, what she
OL,19,Fchooses to wear and when," Apsana
OL,20,Fadded.
