OL,7,FFor these women, it's all about being
OL,8,Fauthentically and unapologetically
OL,9,Fthemselves, even if that means looking
OL,10,Fslightly different or working twice as
OL,11,Fhard to reach the same level as their
OL,12,Fpeers or being victim to hostility.
OL,14,FIf they inspired at least one other
OL,15,Fperson to achieve their goals, then
OL,16,Fthey knew it had been worth it.
